# Ignore build artifacts, bin/obj, IDE files
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/node_modules/
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.log

# Ignore Playwright browser caches (installed during Docker build)
**/.playwright/

# Ignore Docker-specific files from build context
**/Dockerfile
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/.dockerignore
